title: Adobe Acrobat 9 (cracked)
description:
Adobe Systems has now released a new version of its PDF-knowing Acrobat software. Adobe Acrobat 9 now enables users to include Adobe Flash Player compatible video and application files in PDF documents, comes with a concept called PDF Portfolios and access to real-time capabilities for co-navigating PDF documents. PDF Portfolios enable business professionals to assemble multiple media types, such as documents, video, audio, and even 3D objects, into one, compressed PDF file.

www.adobe.com/products/acrobatproextended/
